episodes.title: I Watched Every Anime Made By An Insane Cult
episodes.description:
Ryuho Okawa the super space buddha may be gone from this dimension, but his cult's insane anime legacy will live on forever through this epic three hour mega cut of Geoff Thew's Happy Science roasts. Originally released in three separate parts on @mothersbasement 

Chapters:

00:00 Welcome to Anime Cult Hell
01:47 Hermes: Winds of Love
18:07 The Laws of the Sun
27:39 The Golden Laws
42:55 The Laws of Eternity
1:05:56 The Rebirth of Buddha
1:24:57 The Mystical Laws
1:57:09 The Laws of the Universe SUPERHERO TRILOGY
